{"tid":2047043,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"食西餅要小心，分分鐘幫襯咗吉野家都唔知，超羣係吉野家架！！","createTime":"2020-06-02T00:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T00:26:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3c1450e06efb79d1a18ee4662562185fd55aff","tid":2047043,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:03:30.000Z","msg":"超羣Maria&rsquo;s<br />\n芳叔Uncle Fong<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好諗住「超羣西餅」，係我哋由細睇到大的李曾超羣女仕那個本土品牌，它已經是屬於洪氏家族旗下公司。洪氏家族係乜水？咪就係大家至關心的「香港吉野家」老闆囉。<br />\n<br />\n還有這個什麼「芳叔」，也是屬於「合興集團」。咁合興集團係乜水？係「香港吉野家」及部份「中國吉野家」的控股公司呀！<br />\n<br />\n#超群西餅係藍的<br />\n#超羣西餅係藍的<br />\n#芳叔係藍的<br />\n#又係香港吉野家<br />\n#unclefong<br />\n#maria&rsquo;s<br />\n#marias<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要全世界知道 不要幫襯<br />\n1 小時 &middot; <br />\n錢在荷包， 去什麼地方消費 我有權選擇!<br />\n<br />\n富臨集團又玩換名遊戲!<br />\n🚫大將 (日式火鍋放題)<br />\n將軍澳PopCorn商場<br />\n🚫拌食堂 (蛋包飯)<br />\n銅鑼灣時代廣場<br />\n東涌東薈城<br />\n🚫叉燒丼家 (港式茶餐廳)<br />\n新蒲崗啟德工廠大廈第二期<br />\n葵涌和宜廣場<br />\n元朗 YOHO 1期<br />\n<br />\n🚫甜舍 (甜品)<br />\n元朗 YOHO 1期<br />\n🚫COTI (咖啡)<br />\n觀塘鴻圖道90號<br />\n沙田京瑞廣場二期<br />\n荃灣嘉達環球中心<br />\n🚫柞木炭家 (韓式燒烤)<br />\n旺角TOP<br />\n🚫Caf&eacute; Foodeli (快餐)<br />\n黃大仙新光中心<br />\n🚫炑八<br />\n全港共17間分店<br />\n<br />\n#幫手share<br />\n#我哋要全部人都知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmesAaF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmesAaF.jpg&h=bd6ab6f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ccc1f5a090ddb64859a1c38ec1a5ae6db5a52c6","tid":2047043,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:03:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/eatandtravelhk/permalink/2688830784776418/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Featandtravelhk%2Fpermalink%2F2688830784776418%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=aac70270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/eatandtravelhk/permalink/2688830784776418/</a>"},{"pid":"7030793aeff7bac90b76b90cc